---
title: Sichuan Pork Noodle Soup with Green Beans & Baby Leaves
description: This Sichuan-flavoured soup will warm you up from the inside out! Pork mince, mixed veggies and golden egg noodles all come together in a warm and comforting broth that’s packed full of flavour. Perfect for chilly days, this will fulfill any comfort-food needs.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
